sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant SCH as Scheduler (every 180 min)
    participant SYNC as yandex-sync worker
    participant OAUTH as Yandex OAuth
    participant REP as Direct API Reports
    participant ADS as Direct API Ads.get
    participant DB as SQLite (website.db)
    participant REB as Analytics Rebuild API
    participant UI as Analytics UI/API

    Note over SYNC,OAUTH: One-time token setup
    SYNC->>OAUTH: Exchange auth code for access_token
    OAUTH-->>SYNC: access_token (Bearer)
    SYNC->>DB: Save token metadata (env/config)

    loop Periodic sync (single process, sequential calls)
        SCH->>SYNC: Trigger run
        SYNC->>REP: POST /json/v5/reports (date range, ad stats)
        alt Report queued/in progress
            REP-->>SYNC: 201/202 (processing)
            SYNC->>REP: Poll report status (with delay)
        end
        REP-->>SYNC: 200 TSV report
        SYNC->>DB: Upsert stg_yandex_stats

        opt Metadata enrichment
            SYNC->>ADS: POST /json/v5/ads (Ads.get by ids)
            ADS-->>SYNC: Ad metadata payload
            SYNC->>DB: Upsert ad metadata tables
        end

        SYNC->>DB: Build/update mart tables
        SYNC->>REB: POST /api/analytics/rebuild
        REB-->>SYNC: rebuild status
    end

    UI->>DB: Read prepared marts/datasets
    DB-->>UI: Aggregated analytics data

    Note over SYNC,REP: Error handling: retry/backoff on 429/5xx, single-threaded calls
    Note over SYNC,DB: Incremental mode preferred after first successful full sync
